# Exception: manually-uploaded photos/videos via the Telegram bot's
# /setphoto and /setvideo commands ARE meant to persist in git (they are the
# real, human-curated media, not auto-generated drafts).
!content/images/manual_*.jpg
!content/videos/manual_*.mp4

